Passion, commitment and caring for employees
Spectrum Aeromed is a 26-employee healthcare manufacturing company with a strong focus on company culture. In addition to a robust benefits package that includes a Wellness program and voluntary insurance, Spectrum Aeromed emphasizes a spirit of fun with regular team outings, ski trips, classes, and other activities. The company also uses survey tools to take the pulse of their employees and optimize their offerings based on that feedback.
