IndividualsProducts









Why Aflac?
Aflac is insurance for daily life. We pay cash benefits when you’re sick or hurt to help with expenses not covered by your medical insurance.














Accident Insurance
Accidents Happen. Help protect yourself with a plan that will pay you cash benefits to help with any unexpected expenses.

Learn More Learn More








Cancer Insurance
Give yourself and your family the tools to cope financially if a positive diagnosis of cancer should ever occur.

Learn MoreLearn More








Critical Illness Insurance
Help protect your family from financial burden in the event of a serious diagnosis or injury.

Learn MoreLearn More








Life Insurance
Help find peace of mind with our term life, whole life and juvenile life policies.

Learn MoreLearn More








Hospital Insurance
Get coverage that can help with deductibles, copayments, and other out-of-pocket costs if you’re out of work for a hospital stay.

Learn MoreLearn More








Short-Term Disability Insurance
Maintain a source of income even if you can’t work because of a covered illness or injury.

Learn MoreLearn More








Dental Insurance
Keep smiling with dental coverage that lets you use any dentist you choose.

Learn MoreLearn More








Vision Insurance
Our vision insurance policies help you look sharp and stay focused.

Learn MoreLearn More








