How could an accident impact your lifestyle?
The average cost of a broken leg is $7,352.62% of young adults have less than $1,000 on hand to pay out-of pocket medical expenses.*


What could a broken leg cost you?






187 Date Nights(Based on the AVG Cost of $39.40) 3





28 Music Festivals(Based on the AVG Cost of $261.46) 4





83 Mobile Phone Bills(Based on the AVG Cost of $83.33 monthly) 5









