Aflac - Wikipedia





















 






Aflac

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

Not to be confused with Aflaq or Affleck.

Aflac, Inc.





Type

Public


Traded as
NYSE: AFL
